{"tid":412983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭卓堅申司法覆核 要求DQ何君堯兼取回議員薪金","createTime":"2017-09-25T06:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T23:51:03.000Z","uid":78546,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2fba02b576e380579f3bbf90780952ed6c316e","tid":412983,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T06:40:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170925&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57252632&amp;ref=tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170925%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57252632%26ref%3Dtw&d=mtn6uz1MREFhb02wBKxuT54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=810880b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170925%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57252632%26ref%3Dtw&h=54f0bc4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170925&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57252632&amp;ref=tw</a><br />\n<br />\n長洲居民郭卓堅今就立法會議員何君堯涉虛報資歷而申請司法覆核，指何在立法會選舉時自稱是新加坡和英國及威爾斯執業律師，及後被人發現何無在上述國家有執業律師牌照，認為何繼續利用上述名銜謀取利益，指他違反《選舉（舞弊及非法行為）條例》，要求法庭取消何的議員資格並下令何退還已領的議員薪酬。<br />\n<br />\n繼早前入稟申請取消立法會議員柯創盛、葛珮帆的資格後，郭再就何的資歷申請司法覆核，郭在庭外指「要除三害」，取消三人的議員資格。他相信會有義務律師代表他，至於訟費，他說未能支付就會破產。"},{"pid":"efa3d8edfee94dddcf47121cb3b156886b7cb9ef","tid":412983,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T06:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2bbc9c89bf55a183a83faa7b34c2943d757737f","tid":412983,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:04:08.000Z","msg":"我好興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a7d565afdb150b100e96ca6214402c297e2bbb","tid":412983,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:08:00.000Z","msg":"郭卓堅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"